                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2198" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0074</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9135 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪：民企转型的一匹“黑马”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">BYD: aDark Horse of Private Enterprise Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张莎，李平</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">比亚迪股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">转型模式；企业资源与能力；新能源</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Transformation Mode;Resources and Core Competencies;NewEnergy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本文基于企业转型的相关理论，剖析了比亚迪公司在其发展过程中的内、外部环境变化，以动态分析的视角，对比亚迪公司在不同阶段，采取的转型模式进行深入的案例分析，并归纳出比亚迪公司转型所依赖的资源和核心能力。企业转型不可能天马行空，一定是和自己的某种资源紧密相连。作为我国为数不多的成功案例，比亚迪的转型模式对我国企业的转型具有一些理论意义和现实意义。从理论上讲，这是对我国企业转型相关理论的进一步补充和完善，可以为那些正在寻求转型的企业提供理论依据。从实践意义上讲，案例企业所展现的基于资源和核心能力构建下企业转型的成功经验，可以帮助企业通过对企业文化、创新能力、企业家精神等方面的重视和培养，促进企业核心能力的构建，从而为企业的转型提供现实指导意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Based on the related theories of enterprise transformation, this article analyzes the internal and external environmental changes in the process of BYD’s development, as well as the transformation mode of BYD at different stages in the dynamic perspective,concluding the resources and core competencies the company depends on during the transformation.Enterprise transformation must be closely connected to some resources of the enterprise.As one of the few successful cases, the transformation mode of BYD has some theoretical and practical significancefor the enterprises in China.Theoretically, the transformation mode is the supplement and complement of related theory for enterprises in our country which can provide theoretical basis for enterprises seeking for transformation.Practically, the successful experience of enterprise transformation based on resources and core competence can help enterprises build core competencethrough culture, innovation, entrepreneurial spirit, providing guidance for them.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《战略管理》、《创新与创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业的转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
